# 📝 OpenAI API Configuration Example
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your OpenAI API key.

# 🔑 Must
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# 🤖 Optional
OPENAI_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small  # 或 text-embedding-3-large
OPENAI_MAX_RETRIES=3
OPENAI_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=30

# 💡 Obtaining API Key Steps:
# 1. Visit https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# 2. Log in to your OpenAI account
# 3. Click "Create new secret key"
# 4. Copy the generated API key (starts with sk-)
# 5. Replace "sk-your-openai-api-key-here" above

# ⚠️ Security Reminder:
# - Do not commit your real API key to git repositories
# - Add .env file to .gitignore
# - Regularly rotate your API key
